{"tid":2094895,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳無綫再舉辦歌唱比賽　9月《「聲」夢大賽》吸樂壇新血","createTime":"2020-07-05T05:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:39:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a4df29e90b6ad5cb7d2e27d4e9a436c512e3f91c","tid":2094895,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"無綫（TVB）自2009年舉辦過4屆《超級巨聲》，孕育了不少樂壇新血，更透過另一比賽《星夢傳奇》，發掘公司內具歌唱潛質的藝人，間接促成唱片公司星夢娛樂的成立。<br />\n<br />\n然而近年有不少如許廷鏗、何雁詩等歌手相繼離巢，而繼續留守的胡鴻鈞、吳若希、菊梓喬、連詩雅等則在公司安排下雙線發展，既為TVB推出電視主題曲，亦開始綜藝、電視劇等拍攝工作。有報道指，TVB希望再發掘更多有潛質的歌手，9月將再舉辦《「聲」夢大賽》，在尋找樂壇新力軍的同時，亦為目前缺乏新面孔的電視台補位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200705/356398901542129664.jpeg/7Oz3e6tYxu143uL8d6XHFXHrRSP5JbjMK6zSsius0rI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200705%2F356398901542129664.jpeg%2F7Oz3e6tYxu143uL8d6XHFXHrRSP5JbjMK6zSsius0rI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=5d890802&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1210dc6603363cd5e56646841ac3d6a0a10a08fb","tid":2094895,"uid":42804,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"搞來都冇用。<br />\n一來搞完只會成為tvb廉價勞工，二來社會上對tvb評價越嚟越差，除咗維穩仲有貶低香港本土文化。"},{"pid":"28c4da0b32396347390a49281e24acb977449e3e","tid":2094895,"uid":14983,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"孕育了不少樂壇新血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6350074a5db29a71dd74f2f2614fe61ff52308b","tid":2094895,"uid":68896,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"咪又係淪為比二世祖/中国歌手落嚟入行既踏台階<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380d1ec276c91520edaa7a4de146c05ecd7027f1","tid":2094895,"uid":227597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T